heading: Caldera Gate Dungeon Guide
content: Caldera Gate is an incredibly fast dungeon with no end boss, offering quick clear times for repeated grinding. It also features the highly valuable , which is especially good early on for Hardcore players. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
